Comedian, AY and musician, Timi Dakolo were on hand as The Bridge and Town Houses made its debut in Abuja, the Federal Capital Territory recently. With Nigeria’s current housing deficit statistics still nothing to write home about, Hall 7, a Nigerian real estate company focused on high quality residential and commercial properties, recently completed a luxury project in Nigeria’s capital to improve the data.
The firm invited people to an open house for the project called The Bridge Peridot contains townhouses and apartments. The Bridge Townhouses are so personally designed that the super-delux villa unit gives its owner the option of a fifth bedroom, if they wish. It is such limitless potential in a home that many people look forward to and to have it handed to them in high quality style as Hall 7 Real Estate promises is nothing short of a dream delivered.